{"tid":726884,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】申請GRANT LOAN過左院校DEADLINE","createTime":"2018-07-02T17:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T05:20:30.000Z","uid":148482,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78b7449784dc99c4c2f537215a880d64e8db6002","tid":726884,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:41:06.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲知道點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上星期我收到學資處嘅信話17-18年批到全費<br />\n咁我就鬆左口氣 上網諗住申請埋18-19年(升YR2)<br />\n點知睇到原來4月尾已經過左我讀緊嘅院校嘅Deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為上年係9月頭先申請 冇睇到學校啲Poster<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知道原來在讀生要早啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有差唔多嘅經驗可以教下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經call左去學資處 留左言 仲未有人覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5229a40955f4534eebe00de14b08e644c794fd71","tid":726884,"uid":23815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"留乜撚野言呀<br />\nOFFICE HOUR打去啦"},{"pid":"6aa5c12c202294bc918c4bab2400606880b3233d","tid":726884,"uid":148482,"like":0,"d